&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage all aspects of client selling: prospecting, presenting, proposal generation, relationship management, closing and transition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-Augmented Deal Strategy - Leverage generative AI tools (e.g., Gemini) to conduct deep-dive prospect research, synthesize complex annual reports into actionable value propositions, and draft hyper-personalized outreach at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute territory account plans to achieve and exceed individual&lt;br&gt;quota responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position new opportunities/products and run demos with customized positioning to meet prospective client pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and consistently deliver against an accurately forecasted pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple customer sales cycles and close effectively, including the navigation of negotiations and contracting with procurement teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strong relationships with key decision makers, influencers and partners within identified territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with iSpot’s third party partners to win and maintain business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize customer and prospect contact activities, tools and systems, and update relevant information held in these systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy the iSpot Sales Process to effectively move opportunities through pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage continued trainings offered at iSpot to improve sales results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
